des:
Poop Poop is a fun game requiring both skill and intelligence. Alexa will provide the name of a person, place, or thing, and you have to answer the question: "Does it poop?"

Simply answer "yes" or "no" and see how many you can get correct in a row! At any time you can say "stop" to quit.

This is another classic game brought to Alexa enabled devices by wow.lol. Email atwowdotlot@wow.lol if you have any issues or feedback. We would love to hear from you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
